          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Solid H2 target formed by spraying H2 gas onto a 5.4",
                "mu-m thick cooled Ag foil. The foil adheres to a",
                "copper target cell frame cooled to 4K. The average",
                "thickness was approx. 60 mu-m varying from 30 mu-m to",
                "130 mu-m with time. The target thickness was",
                "continuously measured using the Ag(11Li,11Li)Ag",
                "elastic scattering peak energy of 11Li."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SISD",
                "CSICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The light particles p,d,t were",
                "detected using annular arrays of segmented silicon",
                "strip detectors backed by a CsI(Tl) array. The",
                "silicon detectors with thickness of 100 mu-m served",
                "as dE detector, the total energy was measured using",
                "CsI(Tl) array. This array covered laboratory angles",
                "of theta(lab) from 32 deg to 58 deg."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SISD",
                "SISD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The heavy reaction residues pass",
                "through the hole in the YY1 annular array, and are",
                "detected using a dE - E (60 mu-m and 500 mu-m thick)",
                "double-sided segmented silicon strip detector array",
                "placed further downstream of the target. This",
                "telescope covered laboratory angles of theta(lab)",
                "from 1.8 deg to 5.7 deg."
              ]
            }
          ],
